  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Effect on Recovery of GI Motility and Safety and to Determine the Optimal Dose of LD02GIFRO</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Multi-center, Randomized, Placebo-controlled, Parallel, Phase II Clinical Trial to Assess the Effect on Recovery of GI Motility and Safety and to Determine the Optimal Dose of LD02GIFRO in Patients Undergoing Colon Resection</official_title>
