  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is conducted to determine the optimal dose of LD02GIFRO in improvement of
      gastrointestinal motility between each dose group by comparing the effectiveness and safety
      in patients undergoing colon resection.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
